data.description: Welcome to 43 Bancroft Road! At the end of a long, private drive, this raised ranch home on 5.24 wooded acres offers three bedrooms, two bathrooms, an attached three-car garage with radiant heat, a finished heated basement with a bonus room and 3/4 bath, and an incredible unfinished space primed to add substantial finished square footage! Upon entering, this home opens up into a two-story entry with a coat closet, exposed brick chimney, and direct entry to the attached garage. Upstairs you will find the open-concept kitchen and dining room with wood floors, high ceilings, ample cabinetry and counter space, a picture window for added natural light, and access to the rear screened porch and adjacent patio. The living room is flooded with natural light and finished with a brick wood-burning fireplace. Down the hall is the homes three bedrooms and full bath/laundry room. Downstairs is the finished heated basement with a bonus room, 3/4 bath, and utility closet. Off of the kitchen is a set of stairs that takes you to the unfinished bonus space above the garage. This space is already wired, partially insulated, and ready to be finished by the new homeowners. Beautifully landscaped with perennials and thoughtful flowering bushes around the home. This home offers convenient access to NH Route 119. Only 20 minutes to Peterborough, 30 minutes to Keene, 5 minutes to the Mass border, 75 minutes to Concord/Manchester/Nashua, and 95 minutes to Boston. Showings start Saturday, Jan 21.
